---
---

<section id="about" class="py-24 px-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Section header -->
  <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-12" data-reveal>
    <span class="font-mono text-cyan-400 text-sm opacity-60">01.</span>
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Chi sono</h2>
    <div class="flex-1 h-[1px] bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400/40 to-transparent"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
    <!-- Left: text + stats -->
    <div data-parallax="slow">
      <div class="space-y-4 text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-10">
        <p>
          Sono un <span class="text-white">Frontend Developer</span> con la passione per le
          interfacce curate e il codice pulito. Lavoro principalmente con Angular, React e Astro.
        </p>
        <p>
          Mi piace costruire esperienze web veloci, accessibili e piacevoli da usare,
          prestando attenzione ai dettagli sia a livello visivo che di performance.
        </p>
        <p>
          Quando non scrivo codice, esploro nuovi strumenti, design system e tutto ciò che
          riguarda il mondo del web moderno.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Stats -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 pt-8 border-t border-zinc-800">
        <div>
          <div
            class="text-3xl font-bold text-cyan-400 neon-text font-mono"
            data-count="7"
            data-suffix="+"
          >0+</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-1 font-mono">Anni exp.</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div
            class="text-3xl font-bold text-cyan-400 neon-text font-mono"
            data-count="10"
            data-suffix="+"
          >0+</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-1 font-mono">Progetti</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div
            class="text-3xl font-bold text-cyan-400 neon-text font-mono"
            data-count="5"
          >0</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-1 font-mono">Tech stack</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: info card -->
    <div
      class="border border-zinc-800 rounded bg-zinc-900/60 backdrop-blur overflow-hidden"
      data-parallax="fast"
    >
      <!-- Card header bar -->
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-3 border-b border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900">
        <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-red-500/70"></span>
        <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/70"></span>
        <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500/70"></span>
        <span class="font-mono text-xs text-zinc-500 ml-2">profile.json</span>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 font-mono text-sm space-y-3">
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="text-purple-400">posizione</span>
          <span class="text-zinc-600">:</span>
          <span class="text-cyan-300">"Italia"</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="text-purple-400">disponibilità</span>
          <span class="text-zinc-600">:</span>
          <span class="text-green-400">"open to work"</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="text-purple-400">focus</span>
          <span class="text-zinc-600">:</span>
          <span class="text-cyan-300">"Frontend / UI"</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3 flex-wrap">
          <span class="text-purple-400">email</span>
          <span class="text-zinc-600">:</span>
          <a
            href="mailto:valerio.pinsone@gmail.com"
            class="text-cyan-400 hover:text-cyan-300 transition-colors break-all"
          >
            "valerio.pinsone@gmail.com"
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
